    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Wrap up ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Control W in insert mode. Delete the word behind the cursor. Faster than hammering Backspace."
    },
    {
      "wait": 1.5
    }
